@host = https://localhost:7062
@json = application/json

### Get all students
GET {{host}}/api/students
Accept: {{json}}

### Get student by id
GET {{host}}/api/students/3
Accept: {{json}}

### Create student (POST) — id omitted; server assigns
POST {{host}}/api/students
Content-Type: {{json}}
Accept: {{json}}

{
  "firstName": "New",
  "lastName": "Student",
  "address": "123 Main St, Springfield, IL 62701",
  "dateOfBirth": "2012-07-15",
  "email": "new.student@example.com",
  "phone": "321-555-0199",
  "grade": "7"
}

### Update student (PUT) — route id is source of truth
PUT {{host}}/api/students/4
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "firstName": "New",
  "lastName": "Student",
  "address": "123 Tree St, Springfield, IL 62701",
  "dateOfBirth": "2012-07-15",
  "email": "new.student@example.com",
  "phone": "321-555-0199",
  "grade": "7"
}

### Delete student
DELETE {{host}}/api/students/4
